with the coupon.

23:24.720 --> 23:27.689
And I want you to
keep the wings.

23:27.691 --> 23:30.324
I don't want them.

23:30.326 --> 23:33.194
If you think about
it, it's a win-win.

23:38.269 --> 23:41.404
Unbelievable.

23:41.406 --> 23:42.873
You know what?

23:42.875 --> 23:44.241
Bring the wings.

23:57.691 --> 23:59.892
Why doesn't she come out?

23:59.894 --> 24:02.095
