we stayed by the water

28:47.290 --> 28:49.026
for hours and hours.

28:49.028 --> 28:52.496
I... I thought it was disgusting.

28:52.498 --> 28:55.298
Why would anyone
want to do that?

28:57.202 --> 29:00.639
Since then, we've been on...

29:00.641 --> 29:03.441
I don't know how many...

29:03.443 --> 29:04.809
how many fishing trips.

29:10.618 --> 29:13.553
I've come two of them.

29:13.555 --> 29:13.953
Hm.

29:19.730 --> 29:25.433
He doesn't want
to fish anymore.

29:52.467 --> 29:53.298
Josh.

29:53.300 --> 29:56.569
Officer Moody!

29:56.571 --> 29:58.438
I... I don't think she's home.

30:01.509 --> 30:04.478
