streets alone at night.

30:28.308 --> 30:30.174
She should have a car.

30:30.176 --> 30:31.343
Well, you don't have a car.

30:31.345 --> 30:33.746
You don't even have a license.

30:36.415 --> 30:38.418
I don't need a car.

30:38.420 --> 30:39.318
I've got you.

31:59.680 --> 32:01.913
Let's go
back inside, Arnie.

32:01.915 --> 32:03.749
Everything's fine.

32:03.751 --> 32:05.918
That's not what
it looks like from here.

32:09.025 --> 32:11.592
Have you lost your mind?

32:11.594 --> 32:13.860
