invite you to dinner.

32:32.417 --> 32:34.251
Sure.

32:34.253 --> 32:35.420
Oh, great.

32:35.422 --> 32:37.055
Great.

32:37.057 --> 32:38.355
Just let me know when.

32:38.357 --> 32:39.857
Excellent.

32:39.859 --> 32:41.093
Honey, it's getting late.

32:41.095 --> 32:42.326
You want to go back inside?

32:42.328 --> 32:44.261
Yeah, I probably should.

32:44.263 --> 32:45.597
I think I have a headache.

32:45.599 --> 32:48.400
I'm sure you do.

32:48.402 --> 32:49.235
Good night.

32:55.843 --> 32:56.776
