33:04.086 --> 33:06.287
How is it possible that I...

33:06.289 --> 33:07.456
I'm the one who's wrong?

33:07.458 --> 33:09.991
You're the one who
interrupted me.

33:09.993 --> 33:12.461
I had a perfectly
reasonable fib, darling,

33:12.463 --> 33:14.163
