to come out with,

33:14.165 --> 33:17.132
oh, oh, we would love to
have you over for dinner.

33:17.134 --> 33:18.569
I think to know would be nice.

33:18.571 --> 33:19.902
That's not the point!

33:19.904 --> 33:21.304
That's not the point!

33:21.306 --> 33:23.807
