37:08.268 --> 37:10.601
Um, the mighty Fort Leavenworth.

37:10.603 --> 37:13.371
Phew, it's a huge complex.

37:13.373 --> 37:14.505
Massive.

37:14.507 --> 37:16.608
Fort Leavenworth.

37:16.610 --> 37:19.478
How interesting.

37:19.480 --> 37:21.581
Are you sure you don't know it?

37:21.583 --> 37:22.882
