41:01.536 --> 41:02.501
She's downstairs.

41:02.503 --> 41:03.036
Go ahead.

41:03.038 --> 41:03.869
Thank you.

41:16.686 --> 41:19.121
Jo Ann?

41:19.123 --> 41:19.988
Jo Ann?

41:19.990 --> 41:20.856
Ah!

41:20.858 --> 41:21.724
Oh, oh.

41:21.726 --> 41:24.059
Oh.

41:24.061 --> 41:26.095
You almost gave
me a heart attack.

41:26.097 --> 41:27.030
I'm sorry.

41:27.032 --> 41:28.130
Arnie told me you
were down here.

41:28.132 --> 41:29.300
Oh, that's nice.

41:29.302 --> 41:30.501
Let me make some tea.

41:30.503 --> 41:31.702
Actually, I can't stay.

41:31.704 --> 41:36.574
I just... I wanted to talk
to you about yesterday.

41:36.576 --> 41:38.541
You were following me.

41:38.543 --> 41:39.577
Hm?

41:39.579 --> 41:41.613
You were driving
a car... your car.

41:41.615 --> 41:42.581
My car?

41:42.583 --> 41:44.950
No, I don't even have a license.

41:44.952 --> 41:47.253
A policeman pulled you over.

41:47.255 --> 41:49.389
You ran over the shrubbery.

41:49.391 --> 41:50.222
Oh.

41:50.224 --> 41:52.193
Gee, I hardly remember that.

41:52.195 --> 41:53.293
It's OK.

41:53.295 --> 41:56.162
But I wanted to ask
you not to do that.

41:56.164 --> 41:59.467
Well, look, I'm not
crazy or anything.

41:59.469 --> 42:02.202
A little high-strung,
maybe, but...

42:02.204 --> 42:06.543
oh gosh, how do I say it?

42:06.545 --> 42:08.411
