42:24.798 --> 42:26.465
You looking for Wren?

42:26.467 --> 42:27.766
Yeah, Wren Miller.

42:27.768 --> 42:29.534
Person who lives here.

42:29.536 --> 42:31.405
She in... she in trouble?

42:31.407 --> 42:32.238
No, no.

42:32.240 --> 42:34.842
No, she's not in any trouble.

42:34.844 --> 42:36.677
You know where she is?

42:36.679 --> 42:37.644
Yeah.

42:37.646 --> 42:39.546
She's with my wife.

42:39.548 --> 42:42.883
We older women do
not take to eccentricities,

42:42.885 --> 42:46.153
unless they're our
own or our husbands'.

42:46.155 --> 42:48.824
I'll flush 'em out...
flush 'em out for you.

42:51.996 --> 42:52.729
Come on.

42:52.731 --> 42:55.264
I understand.

42:55.266 --> 42:58.668
So what on God's green
earth are you doing up there?

42:58.670 --> 42:59.670
Jo Jo!

42:59.672 --> 43:02.106
There's a police
officer up here.

43:02.108 --> 43:05.043
He needs to see your
friend for a minute.

43:05.045 --> 43:07.244
Can you send her up?

43:07.246 --> 43:08.713
