change in his pocket.

01:26:04.944 --> 01:26:08.112
I added it all up
yesterday. $1.68.

01:26:11.918 --> 01:26:14.919
It doesn't seem like much.

01:26:14.921 --> 01:26:16.321
It feels good.

01:26:38.048 --> 01:26:39.915
Allison.

01:26:39.917 --> 01:26:43.586
